branchItem.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series PA is a double acting, compact, large capacity diaphragm pump suitable for transfer and recovery of a wide variety of fluids.  The PA series is available in 3 types; automatically  operated, air operated or automatically operated with a built-in pulsation attenuator.  
&lt;/p&gt;

branchItem.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Air operated type process pump with external switching valve&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Easily controlled discharge rate&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Stable operation possible even with a minimal flow rate, low&lt;br&gt;pressure operation or the entrainment of gases&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Can be used when there is repeated stopping of operation&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Longer life than automatically operated type since switching&lt;br&gt;valve is not contained inside the body&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

